[%@lib overflow_error]
[codeblock:synopsis]
namespace std {
  class underflow_error : public runtime_error {
  public:
    constexpr explicit underflow_error(const string& what_arg);
    constexpr explicit underflow_error(const char* what_arg);
  };
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[:en] The class [`underflow_error] defines the type of objects thrown as
exceptions to report an arithmetic underflow error.
[:zh_CN] [`underflow_error] 类定义了作为异常而被抛出的对象的类型，用以报告算术下溢错误。

